# Frontend Conventions

## Stack
- React 18, Vite, Tailwind CSS 3, Lucide React icons
- No state management library — plain useState/useEffect

## Theming
- Light/dark mode via CSS variables defined in `styles.css` and toggled by `ThemeContext`.
- Colors: `#faf8da` (cream/light bg), `#de0136` (accent red), `#221d1e` (dark bg).
- Use `var(--bg-primary)`, `var(--text-primary)`, `var(--accent)`, etc. via inline `style` props for theme-aware colors.
- Tailwind classes for layout/spacing. CSS variable styles for colors.

## Components
- Use component classes from `styles.css`: `.card`, `.btn-primary`, `.btn-secondary`, `.btn-ghost`, `.input`, `.link`, `.badge`, `.table-container`, `.table-header`, `.table-row`, `.table-cell`, `.page-title`, `.section-title`.
- Icons from `lucide-react` only. Always size with `h-N w-N` classes.

## API & Auth
- All API calls go through `api/client.js` which sends `credentials: "include"`.
- On 401 response, the client auto-redirects to the Maya portal login page.
- Data refreshes are triggered by `refreshToken` / `dataVersion` prop from `App.jsx` after sync/clear.

## Pagination
- Default page size: 50 rows.
- Use `ChevronLeft`/`ChevronRight` icons for Previous/Next buttons.
- Show "Showing X–Y of Z" and "page / totalPages" between buttons.
- Search resets to page 0.
